defaultIt would also appear though that more time and effort is being invested in supply side management than in demand side management – i.e. heat (and energy) demand reduc
defaulttion. Domestic and commercial users of energy are interested in reducing the use of heat energy as it in turn reduces their fuel bills but this is proving to be challenging for many. 
